title: Add voice message support
body: This commit adds the new properties for voice messages and functions to the `Attachment` struct. `AttachmentFlags` is also added as an extra.

title: Major updates to dependencies
body:
- bitflags to 2.x
- syn to 2.x
- devise to 0.4.x

title: Fix SelectOption::set_default return type
body: for consistency with the rest of the functions

title: Implement more From traits for MessageResponse
Command sync
body: Adds a way to define command details with the command attribute macro and publish those commands with the bulk overwrite endpoint.

title: Switch format_response to a From trait
Channel rest methods
body: And other stuff that had to be done on the side

title: Attachment options, modals and text inputs
Message rest methods
body: Including some better error handling and updated structs with new API features

It was barely used and basically contained a duplicate dependency of
